CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 12 ,1957, pg. 2 reads: "Hungarian Relief - Members of Friendship Baptist Church included the Hungarian refugees on their Christmas list. Their pastor, the Rev. V.M. Herron, left, presents the check to Miss Anna G. Brand of the refugee resettlement committee at the Council of Churches. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Rev. V.M. Herron, pastor of Friendship Baptist Church, presenting donation to Anna G. Brand for Hungarian refugees, in interior with plaid wallpaper and upholstered wall or booth, possibly in restaurant
